column2: SELECT TOP # f.id, f.ra AS F_ra, f.dec AS F_dec, p.objID, p.ra AS S_ra, p.dec AS S_dec, p.type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z FROM MyDB.FIRST_RADec_Half as f CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (f.ra, f.dec, #) as c JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON c.objid = p.objid
